                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17700711-3-off23 t17700711-3-cd14"></join>, about the hour of one in the night, and stealing a cloth coat, value 20 s. a carving-knife, value 6 d. and four silver tea-spoons, value 4 s. the property of the said 
                     <persName id="t17700711-3-person52">
                        Walter
                         Holland
                     <interp inst="t17700711-3-person52" type="surname" value="Holland"></interp>
